# Attendance — room/class list (Firestore `attendance_rooms` as doc ids r1, r2, …)
# Comma-separated names. Omit or leave empty to use built-in defaults. Restart dev server after edits.
# Upload from terminal: npm run seed:attendance-rooms
VITE_ATTENDANCE_ROOM_NAMES=Room No. 2,Room No. 3,Room No. 4,Room No. 6,Room No. 7,Room No. 8,Room No. 9,Room No. 10,Room No. 11,Room No. 13

# Other Firestore collections: attendance_teachers, attendance_students, attendance_records
#
# If seed:attendance-rooms fails with PERMISSION_DENIED: Firebase Console → Firestore → Rules,
# publish the rules in ./firestore.rules (or run: firebase deploy --only firestore:rules)
#
# Optional: student Excel import — or pass path: npm run import:students-xlsx -- "/path/to/file.xlsx"
# If unset, script tries ~/Downloads/Student data 2025-2026 Session.xlsx then ./data/Student data 2025-2026 Session.xlsx
# STUDENT_IMPORT_XLSX=
